STACYE'S 28th B-day!!!
Ok Everyone... sorry for the delay in this e-mail.... 
It has FINALLY been decided. 
April 8-10th @ Lummi Island for
STACYE'S 28th B-day!!!
 
We will be leaving Friday the 8th around 6pm or so..... It's about a 2 hour drive North.... 15 min past Bellingham.
You take Lummi Island Exit off I5... 
go Left off Exit.
Go Left at Casino.
You'll run right in to a small ferry about 25 miles down the road. It's a 15 car ferry and the cabin is right as you get off the ferry on the left. You wont miss it!!
It's a good idea to bring a tent and sleeping bags just incase, food and of course alcohol. There is a small store on the island but very expensive... plan ahead. It's a full loaded cabin... bathroom, shower, huge kitchen and 2 beds, but a lot of room for people to camp out on floor or yard. 
 The cabin is also right on the beach so beach gear could get fun!!
If you have any questions at all just give us a ring.....
stacye 206.331.2051
brookelyn 206.851.4728
